✅ Zero API fees - runs 100% locally
✅ Memory IS the network - no separate retrieval
✅ Learning happens during inference
✅ Coherence emerges from activation stability
✅ Dual-process is activation pattern difference

**Storage**: Save/load the network weights to disk:
```typescript
saveNetwork() {
  const weights = {};
  for (const [id, node] of this.network) {
    weights[id] = Array.from(node.connections.entries());
  }
  fs.writeFileSync('network.json', JSON.stringify(weights));
}
```

This is TRUE neural architecture - memories fire together during thinking!
